* Description

  This repository is for ChaOS on Samsung Galaxy SIII Mini a.k.a Samsung Golden.
  It's still a work in progress.

* How To Build ChaOS for Samsung Golden

  - Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/chaos
  $ cd ~/chaos


  - Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/thehacka1/android.git -b jellybean-mr2.1

  $ repo sync
  
  If you are having constant errors with repo sync then use either:
  
  $ repo sync -f
  
  or
  
  $ repo sync -j1


  - Setup vendor

  $ ./vendor/cos/get-prebuilts

  - Setup environment and build

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ export USE_CCACHE=1
  $ brunch golden

